707287f-b.title: Brooklyn: Washington Ave. - Atlantic Ave.
707287f-b.text:
Washington Avenue, east side, north from Atlantic Avenue. View 2 and 3 show buildings near Fulton Street. The Trame house is
No. 521.
. N.SSpeTr  August 2S, 1941
